#: addons/barbarians_empire_economy_upgrade.wad/postload.lua:226 input:207
#: input:226 standard
msgid "Smelts iron ore into iron and gold ore into gold."
msgstr "Fon el mineral de ferro en ferro i el mineral d'or en or."

#: addons/barbarians_empire_economy_upgrade.wad/postload.lua:208
#: addons/barbarians_empire_economy_upgrade.wad/postload.lua:227 input:208
#: input:227 standard
msgid ""
"Advanced smelting works needs just one lump of coal to produce 2 iron ingots "
"or 2 bars of gold. The building produces iron and gold faster than a basic "
"smelting works. When there are not 2 pieces of required ore in stock, the "
"building operates as a basic smelting works."
msgstr ""
"Les obres de fosa avançades només necessiten un tros de carbó per produir 2 "
"lingots de ferro o 2 barres d'or. L'edifici produeix ferro i or més "
"ràpidament que una fosa bàsica. Quan no hi ha 2 peces de mineral necessaris "
"en estoc, l'edifici funciona com a obra bàsica de fosa."

#. TRANSLATORS: Performance helptext for a Barbarian production site: Advanced Smelting Works
#: addons/barbarians_empire_economy_upgrade.wad/postload.lua:210 input:210
#: standard
msgctxt "barbarians_building"
msgid ""
"If this building is fully supplied and all metals are needed by the economy, "
"production of four iron ingots and two gold bars takes %1$s on average. If "
"only one kind of metal is needed by the economy, production of one iron "
"ingot takes %2$s on average and production of one gold bar takes %3$s on "
"average."
msgstr ""
"Si aquest edifici està completament proveït i tots els metalls són "
"necessaris per l'economia, la producció de quatre lingots de ferro i dos "
"lingots d'or necessita de mitjana %1$s. Si l'economia només necessita un "
"tipus de metall, la producció d'un lingot de ferro triga %2$s de mitjana i "
"la producció d'una barra d'or triga %3$s de mitjana."

